		<date>2008-12-10</date>
		<license>Apache License 2.0</license>
		<state>stable</state>
		
		<notes>
			Adding support for V6R1 i-Series systems.
			Switch various BINARY/CHAR mismatch bind types for ASCII/EBCDIC.
			DBCLOB added for i5 meta data, etc.
		</notes>
		
